description:
We care about Formula 1 and we want to meet up to watch it together! 

We are a group of F1 fans who gather together to watch races live. Old or new - all Formula 1 fans are welcome. So if you are looking for a place to watch F1 in Stockholm and meet other enthusiast, this is the group for you.
